  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students partition the rectangle into equal parts, but not eight equal parts.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>During the launch of the next day's activity, have students discuss the meaning of <q>sixths</q> and <q>eighths</q>.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>